        "\\&bG-Max Stonesurge\\&f — \\&bAcqua\\&f — \\&3Drednaw",
        "Sparge pietre taglienti sul campo.",
        "",
        "\\&7G-Max Volcalith\\&f — \\&7Rock\\&f — \\&6Coalossal",
